high_descs: Turn left and walk forward then turn left to face the bathroom sink
Pick up the soap bar from the sink
Turn left and walk forward then turn around to face back toward the sink
Wash the soap bar under water in the sink then remove it
Turn right and step away from the sink then turn back toward the tall cabinet just left of it
Open the bottom cabinet and put the soap bar in it
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned soap bar in the bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the tub, then turn left to face the sink.
Pick the bar of soap up off of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn around to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn around to face the cabinet to the left of the sink counter.
Open the lower cabinet door and put the clean bar of soap inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: turn left, head to the sink, take the bar of soap
turn to the left, take a few steps, face the sink
put the bar of soap in the sink
turn on the sink for 3 seconds, take the bar of soap out of the sink
turn around twice, face the dresser, open the door
put the soap in the cabinet, close the door
anns.task_desc: wash the bar of soap for 3 seconds, put it in the cabinet
